        <item>
            <title>2024 亚太区 Predator League 菲国精彩落幕，东道主包办 2 冠</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/20/predator-league-2024/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=predator-league-2024</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/20/predator-league-2024/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 11:00:07 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[acer]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Predator League]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[宏碁]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1215471</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>由 Acer 主办的亚太区 Predator  League 2024 总决赛 1 月 14 日于菲律宾马尼拉圆满落幕，亚洲 26 队参赛精锐团体分别来自香港、日本、韩国、泰国等地，以《DOTA2》、《VALORANT》两款游戏角逐冠军，最终 2 款游戏「Predator Shield」掠夺者盾牌冠军宝座皆由主办国菲律宾包办。据悉 2025 年初将转战马来西亚，势必再掀精彩决赛战局。</p><div style="padding: 56.25% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_8779 2" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/904855533?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script><br />
职业电竞队伍 Oblivion Force 代表香港出征《Valorant》比赛，成功于分组赛事击败台湾代表 RNKKO Esports，可惜仍无缘晋身决赛。是次 Predator  League 2024 比赛《Dota2》及《Valorant》冠军队伍均来自东道主菲律宾，分别为「Team Secret 」及 「Blacklist International 」。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1215944" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240118181953-694x157.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="157" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240118181953-694x157.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240118181953.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲香港代表队 Oblivion Force 以 1:0 战胜台湾代表队 RNKKO Esports<br />
图片来源：<a href="https://www.thespike.gg/match/oblivion-force-rnkko-esports/112333">The Spike</a></p><div style="padding: 56.25% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_8741 2" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/904855667?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script><br />
▲介绍香港代表队 Oblivion Force 出场时刻<br />
得奖参赛队伍讯息如下：</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1216269 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240121124855-694x358.png" alt="" width="694" height="358" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240121124855-694x358.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240121124855.png 1234w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>各队伍台上领奖情况:</h2><div style="padding: 177.78% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_9015" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/904856056?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><div style="padding: 177.78% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_9010" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/904856116?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><div style="padding: 177.78% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_9011" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/904856163?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><div style="padding: 177.78% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_9021" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/904856030?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><div style="padding: 177.78% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_9043" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/904857628?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script><br />
▲完美落幕</p><h2>全场满座有明星歌唱表演</h2><p>除了现场精彩的 Predator League 电竞比赛，Acer 亦邀请了不少偶像团体到场。开幕日有男团 SB 19 成员 Felip 及当地知名女歌手 Ylona Garcia，两人精彩的表演将本来激烈的气氛带至最高点。其后邀请了 Acer 品牌大使 Sarah Geronimo 与 SB19 同台共演；闭幕典礼则邀请了女歌手 KZ Tandingan 与马尼拉交响乐团合奏，让活动完美落幕。</p><div style="padding: 177.78% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_8737" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/904855443?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><div style="padding: 177.78% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_9045" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/904857659?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/15/acer-ces-2024/notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【CES 2024】Acer 推出全新电竞笔电系列　同场加映旗舰显示卡和曲面萤幕</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/12/hornington-outlet/shop_guide/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">汉科圣诞开仓　精选电竞萤幕、手掣、键盘扫货好时机</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>转换品牌形象</h2><p>Acer 泛亚营运总部总经理侯知远表示，「2024 亚太区 Predator League 总决赛精彩落幕，不只展现电竞社群的蓬勃发展，也显示 Predator 产品支援玩家们需求的决心。」</p><p>侯知远又指，今年 Acer 会转换品牌形象，采取更加积极的策略，转为以生活方式主导吸引客人购买 Acer 产品。Acer 会在智能生活产品、AI 解决方案及维修服务方面投放更多资源，为用家提供更优良体验，以吸引更多年轻人留意 Acer 品牌。</p><div style="padding: 56.25% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_8785" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/904855593?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script><br />
▲会场设有游戏试玩及 acer 产品体验</p><div style="padding: 56.25% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_8788 2" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/904855831?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script><br />
▲会场摊位游戏</p><h2>Acer 空清日本成绩爆灯</h2><p>除了电竞、电脑方面的产品外，Acer 亦积极开拓产品线。早前推出的 Acerpure 系列空气清新机亦取得极大成功，营收增长率在日本录得 2670%。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1215948" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/415666473_1511160686-694x520.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="520" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/415666473_1511160686-694x520.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/415666473_1511160686.jpg 1202w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><br />
&nbsp;</p><div style="padding: 177.78% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_8901 2" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/904858003?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><h2>下届 2025 年前进马来西亚</h2><div style="padding: 56.25% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_8724" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/904855738?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/15/acer-ces-2024/notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【CES 2024】Acer 推出全新电竞笔电系列　同场加映旗舰显示卡和曲面萤幕</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/12/hornington-outlet/shop_guide/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">汉科圣诞开仓　精选电竞萤幕、手掣、键盘扫货好时机</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/20/predator-league-2024/game-channel/">2024 亚太区 Predator League 菲国精彩落幕，东道主包办 2 冠</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
